This creates an image to build [Batocera](https://batocera.org/), using Docker.

As example, to build an image for the Raspberry Pi 4, enter through `vagrant ssh` and run:

```
cd batocera.linux
make update-docker-image
make bcm2711-build
```

This takes a long time to finish.

More instructions on the [Batocera Wiki](https://wiki.batocera.org/compile_batocera.linux#easy_compilation).

